name: The Malibu Coffee Table
description: The Malibu Coffee table is the epitome of sleek design and relaxed luxury. Its clean contours, with radiused corners and wide circular legs, mimic the soft, breezy Californian landscape. The rippling Birdseye maple tabletop tinted in a vibrant shade of turquoise echoes the bright sun-drenched colours of the West Coast. The top sits on four wide brushed antique brass legs â€“ the perfect finishing touch to a vignette of sultry charm.
